sentences.english: The 4D adjustable printer head is convenient for printing labels of different materials.
sentences.chinese: 四向位可調式打印頭，便於配合不同標籤材質的應用。

sentences.english: In most cases the printhead will come with a limited time warranty.
sentences.chinese: 在大多數情況下，打印頭會在有限的時間保證。

sentences.english: Measure the printhead gap to the platen.
sentences.chinese: 測量滾筒打印頭的差距。

sentences.english: The more pins a printhead has, the better print quality it can achieve.
sentences.chinese: 打印頭腳越有，更好的打印質量它可以實現的。

sentences.english: Yeah. But we also have a print head for printing our binder materials to solidify the particles.
sentences.chinese: 我們還有一個可以噴射膠黏劑的打印頭。

sentences.english: Squeeze the handle of the Print Head Latch and lift it to release the print heads.
sentences.chinese: 擠壓打印頭卡齒的把子，將其擡起來釋放打印頭。

sentences.english: Squeeze the handle of the Print Head Latch and lift it to release the print heads.
sentences.chinese: 擠壓打印頭卡齒的把子，將其擡起來釋放打印頭。

sentences.english: Having your old printhead rebuilt is in most cases, cheaper than buying a new one.
sentences.chinese: 改建舊有打印頭在大多數情況下，比買新的便宜。

sentences.english: The rebuilt printhead is repaired to meet the manufactures specifications.
sentences.chinese: 打印頭的修復重建，以滿足生產要求。

sentences.english: A faulty printhead cable can cause dots to be missing intermittently.
sentences.chinese: 一個打印頭電纜故障點，以可導致間歇性丟失。

sentences.english: Then realign the print head using the new values by clicking Apply.
sentences.chinese: 然後用新數值重新調整打印頭，單擊“應用”。

sentences.english: The print cartridge of chromatograph integrator is expensive and usually becomes a waste while ink is used up.
sentences.chinese: 色譜數據處理機專用噴墨打印頭是一種高值易耗品。
